node.text:
Would you ride this coaster? 💚 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @earthfever

Sliding through the forests of Borsec in Romania with @ivnicoara 🤪

The new Sunkid Mountain Coaster with its 1,440 metres is one of the longest summer toboggan runs Romania has to offer.

The small town of Borsec with its 2,500 residents is about 50 kilometres to the west of Durau. A popular spa in the times of the Royal and Imperial Monarchy, the place is currently developing an upwards trend. Since this summer, its guests are able to enjoy a new Sunkid Mountain Coaster as well. Tag someone you would share this experience with! 🤯

📽 @ivnicoara
📍 Mountain Coaster Borsec, Romania
🎶 Kaleo - Way Down We Go
